name: NEW! Gorgeous Multi-Colored Trio Necklace
description: This is one of our prettiest designs yet! The Mulit-Colored Trio Necklace is made of 3 delicate strands of magazine beads that are strung from antique brass chain with a simple lobster clasp closure. Every necklace is completely unique and no two are alike. Colors may vary from what is pictured below.

name: Beautiful Mercy House Wall Calendar
description:
Our 12 month calendar features the girls and babies of Rehema House, supported by Mercy House. Each month is personalized with photos for you to enjoy. This is a great way to get to know each of our residents and pray over them.

Calendar measures 8.75"x11" (17.25"x11" open)

name: Lovely 3-Strand Paper Bead Necklace: Variety of Fall Colors
description: These gorgeous 3-strand paper necklaces are the most elegant our Mercy House girls have made so far!  With tiny gold seed beads separating the handmade paper, these necklaces are a conversation starter! They have a simple clasp closure and no two are alike. Colors may vary.

name: 3-Strand Paper Bead Necklace: Variety of Colors
description: These gorgeous 3-strand paper necklaces are the most elegant our Mercy House girls have made so far!  With tiny gold seed beads separating the handmade paper beads, these necklaces are a conversation starter! They have a simple clasp closure and no two are alike. Colors may vary.

name: HandMade Red/Black Animal Print Makeup Brush Bag
description:
These fun makeup brush bags are the perfect accessory for the busy traveler or hard-to-buy-for person in your life.

They are lovingly created by our girls at Mercy House and fit a variety of makeup brushes or can be creatively used to hold pens, pencils, etc.

The wrap and tie with satin ribbon for easy transport and each one have a "Handmade by girls at Mercy House" tag sewn on the inside.

   Soft, comfortable to carry, fits in average purse

路         Holds makeup brushes and eyebrow pencils.

路         Has 6 pockets (2 large, 2 medium and 2 small)

路         Tie closure

路         2" x 8" closed, 8"x9.5" open

name: HandMade Animal Print/Red Aprons
description:
What a special item we have for you! These unique LIMITED EDITION aprons are sewn by our girls at Mercy House.  They are black and white giraffe print with bold red accents.

These would make a wonderful gift for yourself or someone you love.

Each apron has a special tag signifying they were lovingly created by girls at Mercy House Kenya. We hope you love these as much as we do!

Details:
This apron design was tested on a variety of shapes and sizes and would be categorized as a Small/Medium (approximate off the rack dress sizes 2 to 12). It was made to fit the following measurements:
Bust - Between 30" and 38" (76cm and 96cm)
Waist - Between 22" and 32" (56cm and 81cm)
Hips - Between 30" and 38" (76cm and 96cm)

The pattern was adapted from this Modern Vintage Designs: http://www.craftsy.com/pattern/sewing/other/flirty-girl-apron-pattern/18025

Care Instructions:  Machine wash cold on gentle cycle, separately and line dry. Do not bleach. Warm iron as needed.

name: Gorgeous Beauty for Ashes Bags by Freeset
description:
We are thrilled with our brand new bags by Freeset. These gorgeous black jute bags are cotton-lined and have beautiful multi-colored braided straps, a zippered bock and magnetic closure. They are roomy for a purse, diaper bag or carry-all. They are screenprinted with our "chalkboard" theme and coordinate perfectly with our women's shirts.

36 x 36 x 10 cm
14.2 x 14.2 x 3.9 inches

Straps vary in color and might be different shades than pictured. 

About Freeset: Freeset is a fair trade business offering employment to women trapped in Kolkata, India's sex trade. They make quality jute bags, but their business is freedom! Buying this bag supports women in India and Kenya!

name: Beauty for Ashes V-Neck Women's Tee
description:
We absolutely love our new shirts! This is the same popular and comfortable women's v-neck cotton shirt we've sold in the past. This time it's in a gorgeous shade of turquoise with white "chalkboard" writing.

Available in sizes small -Xlarge

name: Navy Blue Unisex "Mercy Made This Happen" Shirts
description:
We are so excited about these awesome new navy blue shirts. These fair trade shirts are sewn by the women of Freeset, so when you purchase one, you are not only helping out Mercy House, you are supporting women rescued from sex trafficking in India!

These shirts are sure to be conversation starters! They will point to the amazing work God has done.

Unisex fit men and women. Please see chart for sizing.

name: Unique Paper Bead Cuff Bracelets
description:
We are excited to introduce our brand new paper bead cuff bracelets with a metal closure. These lovely cuffs are one-of-a-kind and so cute! Please note all items are handmade and no two are the same, so items will vary from pictures.

All cuffs fit average women's size wrist. 

We also have quite a large variety of cuff bracelets that are for the larger wrist. If you'd like one of these, please specify color choice in the notes section when paying.

options.name: large cuff for bigger wrists (specify color preference in note section)

name: Fly High Paper Bird Mobile
description:
These funky, fun dove mobiles are so colorful and appealing! They are a one-of-a-kind creation by our talented artisans. No two are the same, made from 100% recycled items. 

Perfect in any room in the house! Please specify a color range and we'll do our best with our supply. (There is only 1 bird per "mobile", but they are a good size!)

name: Beautiful Funky Paper Bead Earrings
description:
These earrings are so fun! They are big and stylish and match our necklaces perfectly.

Please note that every pair of earrings are completely unique. Size, shape and even color shade will vary from what is pictured.

name: Single Paper Heart Ornament/Adornment
description:
This handmade paper mache heart hangs from string to create a whimsical ornament to hang on a knob or tree! The hearts are made from recycled materials and are completely unique. They measure approximately 4"w, 4"l. 

If you have a specific color request, please make sure you include it in your order, if not, a beautiful random color will be chosen for you.

name: Heart & Wings Women's Fit, V-Neck Shirts
description:
We are so excited about our new stylish women's fit, v-neck shirts. (These are the same quality v-neck t-shirt from our previous popular shirts.) 

The beautiful wings and heart signify how God's eye is on each of one, holding us.

These gray shirts are going to be a huge hit, so get yours today!

Women's fit tees fit to a woman's curves.

name: Love Mercy Silicone Bracelets
description: Share the love and wear mercy! These fun little rubber bracelets are the perfect accessory.

name: Hand-Rolled Paper Coaster Set
description:
This beautiful one-of-a-kind coaster set is handcrafted/ The set of 4 coasters are made from recycled magazines and heavily varnished for waterproofing. Each coaster is completely unique. 

The set comes neatly wrapped in twine and signed by the artist. 

And for a short time, we are offering free shipping in the USA on our coaster sets!

name: Gorgeous Paper Bowls
description:
These beautiful handmade paper bowls are so appealing. They are made 100% from recycled magazines and make quite a statement.

 [They are not food safe and are 100% unique so colors will vary).

name: NEW! Stylish Stretchy Paper Bead Bracelet
description: These cute bracelets are the perfect affordable accessory. Each are handmade paper beads on an elastic bracelet band that stretches over your hand to your wrist, one size fits most.

name: 8x10 Black Framed Rolled Art-Africa, Haiti, China OR Cross
description:
These gorgeous 8x10 black wooden frames with rubbed edges contain a hand-rolled paper mat made by our girls in Kenya. 

Each colorful mat is completely unique, made in Kenya and assembled in America.

Available in the shape of a cross and Africa.
NEW! Now also available in the shape of Haiti and China.

name: Large Funky Paper Bead Necklace-Harvest
description:
Each handmade paper bead is large and is actually several pieces of paper rolled to create the size and unique shape, making a very stylish and fabulous necklace when joined together. 

We have a limited supply of each necklace.
*Please note: Each necklace is 100% unique-no two are the same. 

Shades of colors vary, as do style. Some have small beads in between, others seeds. The shade will between golden yellow and orange. They are all beautiful, but please be aware that your necklace may vary from those pictured.

name: Mercy Shop Gift Certificates
description:
You can now purchase gift certificates to our shop.

Available for $20

You will be emailed a gift certificate to forward to whomever you choose. It will have a one time coupon code that can be entered in the discount box upon checkout.

name: "Don't Make Me Come Up There" Book by Kristen Welch
description:
Dont Make Me Come Up There, published by Abingdon Press. This book is a collection of devotions for busy mothers. It will make you laugh, it will make you cry, it will give you two minutes alone- if youre lucky.

Author proceeds go to Mercy House.
